# Full-Screen Modal Pattern

- Do not place filter or form popups with absolute positioning inside cards when they are modal interactions.
- Use the existing full-screen modal pattern:
  - `v-if` overlay container with `class="modal-overlay"`
  - inner card with `class="auth-card modal-card"`
  - close action in modal footer
- When any modal is open, lock page scroll with:
  - `document.body.style.overflow = "hidden"`
  - reset to `""` when closed or on component unmount
- Prefer one modal state per interaction (for example `showFilterModal`) and wire open/close with explicit handlers.
- Reuse shared modal classes from `frontend/src/style.css` instead of creating ad-hoc floating panel positioning.
